description: An 18 year old man has died following a single vehicle road traffic collision near Dungannon.
title: Dungannon: Teenager dies after crash on Coalisland Road
title_page: Dungannon: Teenager dies after crash on Coalisland Road - BBC News
maintext:
An 18-year-old man has died following a single car crash in County Tyrone, police have said.
It happened on the Coalisland Road, near Dungannon, on Tuesday night.
"Police received a report shortly after 22.50 GMT, that a black Peugeot 207 had been involved in a collision," said Insp Cherith Adair.
"The driver of the vehicle was taken to hospital where he sadly passed away." The Coalisland Road remains closed at this time.
